The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 Bangla 4-0 up

Dhaka: Bangladesh moved to within one win of a series sweep over Zimbabwe after they eased to an eight-wicket victory over the tourists in the fourth match at Mirpur Stadium on Friday. 

An unbeaten 58 by Man of the Match Aftab Ahmed helped Bangladesh to 147 for two in 32.2 overs after the visitors managed just 146. 

 (REUTERS) 




